(3, '3. What are the different modes of payment available?', '   You can use any one of the following payment methods:     Credit card,     Credit card EMI of leading banks,     Debit card,     Net Banking,     Cash on Delivery.'),
(4, '4. what is price check?', '  price check service is a no obligation quote to compare the vehicle that you are in the market to purchase to see if you are really getting a good deal.'),
(5, '5. How can I cancel my order?', 'Click on \"Cancel Order\" below. Choose the order, select the reason and submit!'),
(6, '6. Check status of the order.', ' You can check your current order status by simply logging into your account. This lets you track your order in real time. Alternatively, you may check the status of your order     by calling our Customer Service number:'),
(7, '7. How you deliver the order?', '    Your order will be delivered by EMS or Courier, depending on your pincode.');
